Package: epidscan
Type: Package
Title: Modular SatScan Pipeline for Epidemiological Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Songyos Rajborirug <songyos.r@psu.ac.th>
Maintainer: Songyos Rajborirug <songyos.r@psu.ac.th>
Description: A modular pipeline for preparing data and running SatScan analyses for disease surveillance. Provides tools for processing geographic, population, and case data, generating SatScan input files, and post-processing results.
